commands.params_yaml: directory: src
directory: src

script: |
    set -o errexit
    mkdir mongodb
    cd mongodb
    curl ${mongo_url} -o mongodb.tgz
    tar xvf mongodb.tgz
    chmod +x ./mongodb-*/bin/*
    mv ./mongodb-*/bin/* .
    mkdir -p db_files

background: true
script: |
    ./mongod --dbpath ./db_files &
working_dir: mongodb

script: "cd mongodb \n./mongo --nodb --eval 'assert.soon(function(x}{try{var d = new Mongo(\"localhost:27017\"}; return true}catch(e}{return false}}, \"timed out connecting\"}'\n"
working_dir: mongodb

script: |
    . ./set_gopath.sh
    set -e
    go test -v > logkeeper.suite
type: test
working_dir: src
